id: pmc-8t9f
title: Relax changelog title escaping for readable Markdown
description: "Fix downstream pm-cli pm-3299: generated changelog entry titles over-escape harmless GitHub Markdown characters, including parentheses and intra-word underscores such as EXTENSION_AUTHOR_CONTRACTS. Keep strict escaping for IDs, metadata, links, and body previews while using title-context escaping for item titles."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: changelog,downstream-pm-cli,markdown
